<Sect1 id="sec-ShowFunctions">
<Title><literal>ShowFunctions</literal>
<IndexTerm>
  <Primary>ShowFunctions</Primary>
  <secondary>library</secondary>
</IndexTerm>
</Title>

<Para>
The <literal>ShowFunctions</literal> module contains the following
instance of <literal>Show</literal> for function types

<programlisting>
instance Show (a -&gt; b) where
	showsPrec _ _ = showString "&lt;function&gt;"
</programlisting>
<IndexTerm>
  <Primary><literal>Show</literal></Primary>
  <secondary>instance for functions</secondary>
</IndexTerm>

</para>
</sect1>
